Interface FullBinaryMemcacheRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    @UnstableApi
public interface FullBinaryMemcacheRequest
extends BinaryMemcacheRequest, FullMemcacheMessage
    A BinaryMemcacheRequest that also includes the content.
